external_knowledge:
- 'blossoming members' refers to users who are not banned and have the role of 'member';
- 'planted more than five posts' refers to users who have posted more than 5 times;
- 'sunbeams (likes)' refers to the number of likes a post has received.

- "Popular" refers to topics with a high number of views by members;
- "Public and open topics" means topics that are not private (visible to all) and not locked (new posts are allowed);
- "More than 5 posts" filters out less active topics to focus on more engaged discussions.

- "The 10 most prolific gardeners" refers to the top 10 users based on the number of posts and views;
- "Seeds they've sown" refers to the topics they have started;
- "Harvest they've reaped" refers to the total posts and views on those topics.

